<REPLACE-DEFINITION	PLAYER <CONSTANT PLAYER PROTAGONIST>>
<REPLACE-DEFINITION	PRINT-INTQUOTE <CONSTANT PRINT-INTQUOTE 0>>
<DELAY-DEFINITION	REFRESH>
