<REPLACE-DEFINITION SEE-VERB?
	<ROUTINE SEE-VERB? ()
		 <VERB? CHASTISE COUNT EXAMINE FIND TAKE
			;INVENTORY LOOK LOOK-BEHIND LOOK-DOWN LOOK-INSIDE
			LOOK-UNDER READ SEARCH>>>

<COMPILATION-FLAG P-APOSTROPHE-BREAKS-WORDS <>>
